This toothpaste is clinically proven to be 4X more effective at removing plaque, the main cause of gum problems. It is specially formulated with 67% specialized mineral salts that physically remove the build-up of plaque bacteria on teeth and along the gum line. This toothpaste has a unique taste that keeps your mouth feeling fresh and clean.- A daily fluoride toothpaste that provides daily protection against gum problems- Formulated with 67% specialized mineral salts to physically remove the build-up of plaque bacteria- Designed for daily use to take care of your gums and also strengthen teethAbout the Brand: Parodontax has a long history of protecting gum health.
